        到這邊、移動到剛才作的「myapp」。
<br><br>
        <strong>terminal</strong>
        <br>
        <small><i class="fa fa-windows color-blue"></i>　使用Windows的話，請使用「命令提示符」。</small>
<table class="highlight">
<tr>
<td class='code-line-no text-center'>1
</td>
<td class='code-content'><span class='code-line'>cd myapp</span>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<br>
        <%= link_to image_tag("https://s3.amazonaws.com/rails-textbook/rails_for_sfc/images/page3/Terminal_cd_myapp.png",
                              :width => "90%",
                              :class => "hover_img textbook-title-img"),
                    "https://s3.amazonaws.com/rails-textbook/rails_for_sfc/images/page3/Terminal_cd_myapp.png",
                    :target => ["_blank"] %>
        <strong>那麽，導入工具吧！請打入下面的文字。</strong>
        <br>
        <small>※　用半母字母數字打入。</small>
<br><br>
        <strong>terminal</strong>
        <br>
        <small><i class="fa fa-windows color-blue"></i>　使用Windows的話，使用「命令提示符」</small>
<table class="highlight">
<tr>
